{
  "texts": [
    "In fact, rubric-based verifiers are already deployed in challenging IF benchmarks (Zhou et al., 2023; He et al., 2024; Deshpande et al., 2025).",
    "However, developing a scalable learning pipeline for advanced IF still faces several challenges:",
    "• Lack of high-quality rubrics for evaluations: Most of the existing benchmarks either have LLM-generated prompts or LLM-generated rubrics.",
    "• Reliable rubric generator and verifier.",
    "Given a user prompt from the large-scale training data where human labeling is impractical, we need a generator to synthesize corresponding rubrics to evaluate the response, and a verifier to judge whether a response complies with the rubric."
  ]
}